@startuml

actor Admin
participant "Admin Dashboard" as Dashboard
participant "WCMS Backend" as Backend
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Google Maps API" as Maps
participant "Driver App" as Driver

Admin -> Dashboard: Create/Update Route
Dashboard -> Backend: Send Route Details
Backend -> Maps: Request Route Optimization
Maps -> Backend: Return Optimized Route
Backend -> DB: Save Route
Backend -> Driver: Send Route Assignment
Driver -> Driver: View Assigned Route

@enduml
